{"id":19,"parent_id":0,"book_id":23525,"content_id":1,"language_id":0,"display_order":19,"title":"Why is it important not to be jealous of others?","subtitle":"By Elder Jeffrey R. Holland","short_title":"Why is it important not to be jealous of others?","uri":"/friend/2013/08/why-is-it-important-not-to-be-jealous-of-others","content":[["div",{"id":"container","role":"main"},["div",{"type":"article","uri":"/friend/2013/08/why-is-it-important-not-to-be-jealous-of-others"},[".heading",{"id":"head1","uri":"/friend/2013/08/why-is-it-important-not-to-be-jealous-of-others.head1"},[".seriesTitle","Special Witness"],["h1","Why is it important not to be",["span.dominant","jealous"],"of others?"],[".byline",["p.para",{"id":"p3","uri":"/friend/2013/08/why-is-it-important-not-to-be-jealous-of-others.p3"},"By Elder Jeffrey R. Holland"],["p.para",{"id":"p4","uri":"/friend/2013/08/why-is-it-important-not-to-be-jealous-of-others.p4"},"Of the Quorum of the Twelve Apostles"]],[".event",["p.para",{"id":"p5","uri":"/friend/2013/08/why-is-it-important-not-to-be-jealous-of-others.p5"},"From “The Laborers in the Vineyard,” and",["span.emphasis","Ensign,"],"May 2012, 31–33."]],["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/leaders/jeffrey-r-holland.jpg"}],[".kicker","The members of the Quorum of the Twelve Apostles are special witnesses of Jesus Christ."]],[".bodyBlock",[".figure",{"id":"f56","uri":"/friend/2013/08/why-is-it-important-not-to-be-jealous-of-others.f56"},["img",{"src":"http://www.lds.org/bc/content/shared/content/images/leaders/fr13aug27-special-witness.jpg"}],[".credit",["p.para",{"id":"p7","uri":"/friend/2013/08/why-is-it-important-not-to-be-jealous-of-others.p7"},"Illustration by Craig Stapley"]]],["p.para",{"id":"p8","uri":"/friend/2013/08/why-is-it-important-not-to-be-jealous-of-others.p8"},"We are not in a race against each other to see who is the wealthiest or the most talented or the most beautiful or even the most blessed."],["p.para",{"id":"p9","u